node.text:
Sičhona: Dakota word for “Barefoot”

Introducing @pharrell’s @humanrace Sičhona, designed to capture the feeling of being connected to the earth beneath you. This new silhouette is a call to the world to experience and learn more about the Dakota land and its people. The “I am Dakota, We are Dakota” campaign was shot by, creatively directed by, and features a cast made up of Dakota and Indigenous people. 

In partnership with Pharrell, we will be funding a 10kW solar array training and demonstration project that will produce clean energy for a community center focused on the youth of Standing Rock.

Launching on August 27th, the first drop of the Humanrace Sičhona is available globally on adidas Confirmed and via select retailers. 

--
